snippet.title: Bug & Seek | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Become a Master Bug Hunter in this cozy bug-catching simulator, styled like an 8-bit classic. You’ve bought the local bug museum, abandoned after a mysterious robbery. Fill orders, build your collection, and upgrade your skills and equipment while exploring Buggburg and uncovering its secrets.

Play the demo on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2265310/Bug__Seek/

The Official Gameplay Trailer for Bug & Seek, coming soon to Steam and Nintendo Switch.

Music by @AxletreeMusic  https://freemusicarchive.org/music/Axletree/
"Goldfinch: Flight to the North (Remastered)" from Free Music Archive. License CC BY.
